&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Competency Requirements (Junior MySQL Operations Engineer) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with mainstream AI coding assistants (e.g., Claude Code, ChatGPT, Gemini) and able to leverage them for day-to-day operations tasks such as SQL optimization suggestions, troubleshooting, and documentation generation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capable of writing effective prompts and iteratively refining them based on model outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aware of AI model limitations and maintains a habit of manually validating results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has hands-on experience using AI tools to address real MySQL operations scenarios, such as slow query analysis, parameter tuning recommendations, and incident diagnosis assistance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands the fundamentals of RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) and is able to structure database operations knowledge into AI-consumable formats, such as knowledge bases, tuning case libraries, and FAQ documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has exposure to AI application frameworks such as LangChain or LlamaIndex, or has basic experience with vector databases (e.g., Qdrant, pgvector).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands the basics of MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration and is familiar with how AI Agents interact with external tools Maintains a habit of organizing day-to-day operations experience into structured documents or prompt templates for team-wide sharing and reuse.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in Mandarin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing MySQL / Percona Server 8 at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing distributed database, like Clickhouse, Hbase, MongoDB and Starrocks etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Percona tools, Orchestrator, Ghost etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
